        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在150°C和500 psi条件下，使用不同载体（HY、HM、Al2O3、SiO2、TiO2）负载的Pt和Pd单金属催化剂以及Pt-Pd双金属催化剂，对1-萘酚进行选择性加氢，生成四氢萘酚（THNol）异构体（1,2,3,4-THNol和5,6,7,8-THNol）以及其他产物如四氢萘（THN）和脱氢产物。研究了不同载体、金属类型、Pt/Pd比例、反应时间和压力对转化率和选择性的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Supported Pt and Pd catalysts were examined for selective hydrogenation of 1-naphthol to form tetrahydronaphthol (THNol)... Catalytic tests were done in a 25ml stainless-steel microautoclave reactor. The reactor was charged with 0.05g catalyst, 0.5g 1-naphthol (TCI, 99.99%), and 2.0g of n-tridecane solvent... All reactions were done under 500psi at 150°C...",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
